:::comment
Both of these types are in {lean}`Type 2`:
:::

これらの型はどちらも {lean}`Type 2` に存在します：

```lean
example (α : Type 1) (β : Type 2) : Type 2 := α → β
example (α : Type 2) (β : Type 1) : Type 2 := α → β
```
